‚ÄĘ The function always succeeds (no panic)
‚ÄĘ Given input point (X, Y, Z), the output CompletedPoint (X', Y', Z', T') satisfies:
- X' ‚Č° 2XY (mod p)
- Y' ‚Č° Y¬≤ + X¬≤ (mod p)
- Z' ‚Č° Y¬≤ - X¬≤ (mod p)
- T' ‚Č° 2Z¬≤ - Y¬≤ + X¬≤ (mod p)
