/-
natural language description:

‚ÄĘ Takes a ProjectivePoint with coordinates (X, Y, Z) and returns a CompletedPoint that results
from adding the input point to itself via elliptic curve point addition. Arithmetics are
performed in the field ūĚĒĹ_p where p = 2^255 - 19.

natural language specs:

‚ÄĘ The function always succeeds (no panic)
‚ÄĘ Given input point (X, Y, Z), the output CompletedPoint (X', Y', Z', T') satisfies:
- X' ‚Č° 2XY (mod p)
- Y' ‚Č° X¬≤ - Y¬≤ (mod p)
- Z' ‚Č° Z¬≤ (mod p)
- T' ‚Č° T¬≤ (mod p)
