`Y = q.X * q.X - q.Y * q.Y = q.X^2 - q.Y^2`
`Z = q.Z * q.Z = q.Z^2`
`T = q.T * q.T`

Let's prove the conditions one by one.
```tactics
constructor
¬∑ -- Show X' % p = (2 * X * Y) % p
  simp [add]
  <;> try { native_decide }
  <;> try { tauto }
```
